      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NANCY DEVERE (2) last few starts have been well off top, the latest finishing 4th (35.35) in a Grade 5 at Sandown. Goes very well at course and distance boasting two wins. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and four minor placings to her credit. Better than the latest effort and deserves another chance. HAPPY DAD (8) is rarely far away but tends to find one better, placing 10 from 21 starts. Has hit the frame at his last three runs, the latest finishing second (34.77) at this track. Form from his last run is proving to be solid. Will give a great sight again. HECTOR DARCY (6) was prominent throughout when winning in the fastest time of the card two back but could manage only midfield last time when finished 4th and beaten 5 lengths at this track (35.00). Solid formlines coming through his last run. Has the ability to give this a shake. MAGIC SCOTCH (1) is in the mix despite missing out at this track last time.",
